Setting.Description:
Determines the default scope that the search should pick when the request is opened. Default is set to 'At OSU Libraries only'. Other options available are listed here:
For 'Books, media and articles' enter: 'scope:(OSU),scope:(P),scope:(E-OSU),primo_central_multiple_fe',
for 'At OSU Libraries only' enter: 'scope:(OSU),scope:(E-OSU)',
for 'OSU Libraries + Summit' enter 'scope:(OSU),scope:(P),scope:(E-OSU)',
for 'Special Collections and Archives' enter: 'scope:(OSU_SCARC)',
for 'Articles' enter: 'primo_central_multiple_fe',
and for 'OSU Cascades' enter: 'scope:(OSU_CASCADES)'
